parameters:
Yui: "What's with the cool face saying welcome back. What are you
planning by dragging Ginga into this?"
Polka: "I need to talk to Yui-chan as well."
Polka: "Soon, I will be entering a long sleep."

Polka: "Maybe it's the price for only my soul being resurrected in
this era... It seems like this body is reaching its limit."
Polka: "That's why I asked Ginga, the one you trust the most."
Polka: "Yui-chan, no... I want you to support Pony-Celeste."

Yui: "But Ginga doesn't have the power of Pony-Celeste... the sacred
power."
Yui: "There's no way he can stand against Zaida-G..."

Polka: "Even without the sacred power, he will surely be of help to
you."
Polka: "You must have started to realize it after today's events."

Polka: "The source of sacred power is love. True power is unleashed
when there is someone you love."

Polka: "Ginga is your precious person, and you are Ginga's...
irreplaceable to each other."

Polka: "That look on your face, it seems like feelings have already
been conveyed."
Polka: "Hehe, now all that's left is to take action."
Yui: "What!? What do you mean by 'take action'...?"
Polka: "Hehehe, you know what I mean."

Polka: "You are already a splendid warrior of light. Even without me,
I'm sure you can defeat Darg-Noir and bring about peace."
Polka: "In the end, I've pushed everything onto Yui-chan..."

Yui: "That's not true! If it weren't for Polka, by now we would have
been at the mercy of Zaida-G..."

Yui: "I don't want you to go away. We've finally become good friends,
it's too cruel."

Yui: "Once it's peaceful, I wanted to have more silly conversations
with Polka!"
Polka: "Those words mean a lot to me."
Ginga: "Looks like he's entered deep sleep time."

Ginga: "If he eats a lot, he gets hit with sleepiness more than
others. Given the tremendous amount of food he's had recently, he
might not wake up for a few days."

Yui: "Entering a long sleep... you mean he's overcome with drowsiness
because he's full?"

Yui: "Could it be that the reason why the fridge has been empty lately
is..."
Ginga: "He's been incessantly begging me to cook for him..."

Yui: "So he dumps all the work of justice on me and he's comfortably
sleeping off a full belly!?"
Yui: "Huh? Huh? Huh~~? Don't mess with me---!!"
Ginga: "I mean, you're telling me this because...?"
Yui: "I'm telling you to wake up, Polkaaa---!!"
Ginga: "Now, now, calm down... Polka must have his reasons..."
